**Query #1**

    SELECT SEM, SEC, GENDER, COUNT(*)
        FROM STUDENT S, SEMSEC SS, CLASS C 
        WHERE S.USN = C.USN AND 
        SS.SSID =C.SSID 
        GROUP BY SEM, SEC, GENDER 
        ORDER BY SEM;

| SEM | SEC | GENDER | COUNT(*) |
| --- | --- | ------ | -------- |
| 2   | B   | FEMALE | 1        |
| 3   | A   | MALE   | 1        |
| 4   | C   | MALE   | 1        |
| 8   | C   | FEMALE | 1        |
| 8   | D   | MALE   | 1        |

