**Query #2**

    SELECT *
        FROM STUDENT S, SEMSEC SS, CLASS C 
        WHERE S.USN = C.USN AND 
        SS.SSID = C.SSID AND 
        SEM = '4' AND SEC='C';

| USN     | SNAME | ADDRESS  | PHONE     | GENDER | SSID | SEM | SEC | USN     | SSID |
| ------- | ----- | -------- | --------- | ------ | ---- | --- | --- | ------- | ---- |
| 18CS001 | AKASH | MANGLORE | 987654321 | MALE   | 113  | 4   | C   | 18CS001 | 113  |

